data.name: Label4.Text
data.value:
Connecting Your HotBox: 1. Make sure there is no power connected to the sense wire on your meter and it is currently powered off. 2. Connect a micro USB cable from your HotBox to your PC. 3. Once your HotBox shows "Programming Mode" on the display press the "Scan Ports" button. 4. Select the COM port assosiated with your HotBox. 5. Upload images and modify settings to your heart's desire.
There is no limit on custom.
